name: <sync::once_lock::OnceLock<T> as core::cmp::PartialEq>::eq

sync::once_lock::OnceLock::<T>::get.doc:
Gets the reference to the underlying value.

 Returns `None` if the cell is uninitialized, or being initialized.
 This method never blocks.

core::cmp::PartialEq::eq.doc: Tests for `self` and `other` values to be equal, and is used by `==`.
